metadata.name: Still Searching
metadata.description:
It's been so many years
Yet I'm here, still in tears
Your whisper on my ears
I'm trying but never disappears

Do you still watch the night sky?
Do you still dream and wanted to fly?
I will never want to see you cry
'Cause you are my one and only guy

It's been years and I'm still crying
My heart was still breaking
I will never stop searching
Remember, you are my everything

-
